snippet.title: Cognition Game Of The Year Edition Trailer
snippet.description:
Phoenix Online Studios proudly presents Cognition Game Of The Year Edition. This brand new Cognition update presents all four episodes with developers commentary, development videos and plenty more behind the scenes content.
